Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.84,0:00:04.21,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Encounters are mysterious!\NBut cases are even more so!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.21,0:00:06.28,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I'm so glad I'm with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.28,0:00:08.15,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Today's stage is a regular apartment building!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.15,0:00:10.02,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}All the players are set in front of Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.02,0:00:11.75,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.75,0:00:13.69,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.69,0:00:16.26,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.88,0:01:50.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! Kozaburo Hijikata{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, the historical drama actor?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.05,0:01:53.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep! He should be here soon to see me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.62,0:01:57.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, he's going to play a detective on TV next,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.33,0:02:01.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so he wants to hear what this great detective thinks about things!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.40,0:02:03.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.30,0:02:05.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.00,0:02:09.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? But I thought he only did historical dramas...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.47,0:02:13.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look at me. He seems to be on the decline lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.67,0:02:17.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he has no other choice?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.55,0:02:21.30,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Hijikata Kozaburo (51)\NActor
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.75,0:02:21.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So sorry I'm on the decline.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.42,0:02:24.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kozaburo Hijik...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.79,0:02:28.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not so loud, Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.19,0:02:32.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The press has ears everywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.43,0:02:33.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Press?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.43,0:02:37.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, because of the fuss about your divorce with your wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.43,0:02:39.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Divorce?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.07,0:02:42.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, it's completely unfounded! It's a bunch of baloney.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.67,0:02:45.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even my wife Isami is troubled by it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.47,0:02:48.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just some small talk with a dapper man
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.14,0:02:50.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,has everyone exclaiming, "Affair!" and, "Breakup!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.41,0:02:56.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped. You did choose a beautiful actress as your wife!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.55,0:03:05.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, in any case, let's finish up here and head to my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.36,0:03:07.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.53,0:03:09.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.47,0:03:19.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right this way, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.21,0:03:21.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop it; I'm no "Sensei"...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.98,0:03:27.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hoping you can educate me in the finer points of detective work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.18,0:03:29.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So "Sensei" definitely fits!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.08,0:03:32.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess when you put it like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.12,0:03:40.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. Why do we hafta sneak in from the back?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.60,0:03:44.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The front entrance is often swarming with reporters.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.34,0:03:50.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.61,0:03:56.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Looks like there's no one today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.71,0:03:59.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If they happened to see me with a detective
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.15,0:04:02.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,while all this divorce nonsense is going on,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.25,0:04:05.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,who knows what they would write next!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.89,0:04:07.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.99,0:04:16.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?! Aren't you Hajime Okita{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, the actor?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.46,0:04:17.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.83,0:04:20.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's my next-door neighbor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.74,0:04:23.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Headed out?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.07,0:04:25.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. To the convenience store.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.34,0:04:30.31,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Hajime Okita (29)\NActor
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.44,0:04:32.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I'll be waiting for you in my place just like we agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.78,0:04:36.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"Agreed"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.12,0:04:40.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd talk to him about you-know-what.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.72,0:04:43.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's "you-know-what"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.79,0:04:50.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Rumor is he's the guy Hijikata{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s wife is having an affair with.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.26,0:04:52.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.03,0:04:53.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, get in!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.87,0:04:55.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.27,0:05:01.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come to think of it, I haven't given you my card yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.71,0:05:03.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.38,0:05:05.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And one for you, little boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.28,0:05:08.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You certainly seem to own many apartments!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.95,0:05:11.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All the ones on the 6th floor, even!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.35,0:05:16.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I used to use them as offices and rent them to people,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.89,0:05:19.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but they're empty now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.43,0:05:24.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But we're headed to the 5th floor now, where I live.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.90,0:05:27.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! And here we are!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.11,0:05:35.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.75,0:05:40.13,Dialogue Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Hijikata"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.78,0:05:39.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.78,0:05:41.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.92,0:05:44.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, welcome, Mr. Detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.42,0:05:46.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.12,0:05:48.66,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Wow! Isami Nagakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.66,0:05:51.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for coming all this way today for my husband!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.55,0:05:53.31,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Isami Nagakura (38)\NCurrent Family Name: Hijikata\NKozaburo Hijikata's wife
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.79,0:05:54.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please teach him well!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.86,0:05:58.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, he only knows how to swing swords around!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.37,0:05:59.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.80,0:06:05.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You get along well! Where did this marital strife rumor ever start?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.07,0:06:09.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly! We should invite the person who wrote that article over!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.58,0:06:12.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The newspapers just find it amusing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.71,0:06:16.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, right this way! Come on in!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.96,0:06:23.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Start by relaxing in the living room!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.06,0:06:25.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.00,0:06:32.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Brilliant acting, just what I'd expect from a former actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.80,0:06:34.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You hardly seem like a wicked woman
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.80,0:06:38.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,trying to swipe a big sum of compensation money from her husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.51,0:06:42.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but it was {\i1}your{\i0} flirtatious tendencies that started it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.84,0:06:44.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, once you cut loose from me,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.68,0:06:47.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,are you planning to hook up with that lowlife Okita?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.92,0:06:50.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. I haven't planned that far.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.39,0:06:55.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you wait in here a bit, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.36,0:06:57.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, don't worry about us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.93,0:07:08.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyways, what are you doing, bringing a detective here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.77,0:07:13.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you, me, and Okita{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} were going to talk this evening?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.51,0:07:16.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what you want to talk about at this point, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.78,0:07:22.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, don't be like that.\NI have my own circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.05,0:07:24.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been a bit strange lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.62,0:07:28.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Suddenly redecorating and cleaning the place...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.09,0:07:31.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not my fault. I have nothing to do now that I've lost my livelihood.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.49,0:07:34.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyways, I leave that detective to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.96,0:07:38.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be waiting in the office! Hurry it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.20,0:07:40.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.23,0:07:42.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was planning to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.54,0:07:47.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's taking Hijikata{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.17,0:07:50.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been half an hour now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.14,0:07:52.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, what could he be doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.22,0:07:57.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? It won't light.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.95,0:08:01.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's time you give up smoking?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.96,0:08:05.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.53,0:08:07.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?! A gun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.83,0:08:10.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be dumb! This is a lighter!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.30,0:08:15.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You pull the trigger like so and the flame comes out of the barrel!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.14,0:08:18.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Darn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.01,0:08:25.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,T-The trigger broke!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.65,0:08:31.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.39,0:08:36.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My wife usually takes care of this, so it took me a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.92,0:08:40.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Did Isami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.56,0:08:44.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Said she was going to a friend's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.16,0:08:50.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes! I bought something I was hoping you'd teach me about!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.10,0:08:54.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? That's strange. I'm certain I left it here...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.78,0:08:56.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Left what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.58,0:08:59.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A model gun. It was quite pricey, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.98,0:09:02.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The detective I'm going to play is a flashy one
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.98,0:09:06.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,who wears disguises and shoots guns, you see!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.59,0:09:09.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was hoping you could show me how to hold a gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.99,0:09:12.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need anything like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.36,0:09:17.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, TV detectives these days don't carry guns!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.03,0:09:19.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You should strive for realism!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.53,0:09:22.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But that'd be much weaker...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.94,0:09:26.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear the first scene starts with a shootout between me and the killer
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.14,0:09:28.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,on this very riverbank...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.01,0:09:29.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Riverbank?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.01,0:09:30.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.58,0:09:35.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See? Right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.15,0:09:37.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! What a lovely view!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.82,0:09:41.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This must be quite a nice view at night, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.32,0:09:43.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The charm wears off before too long!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.39,0:09:46.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so nice having a river right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.83,0:09:49.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.43,0:09:51.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? It's coming from over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.50,0:09:53.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Okita's phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.60,0:09:55.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Then that's Okita{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.84,0:10:00.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. That's more reason why the reporters stir up trouble here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.52,0:10:13.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Isami!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.12,0:10:16.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What happened?! Isami! Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.36,0:10:18.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're on the 5th floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.33,0:10:19.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.93,0:10:24.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That lowlife! What did he do to my Isami?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.04,0:10:27.00,Dialogue Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Okita"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.50,0:10:27.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Okita! Get out here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.47,0:10:30.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okita! Okita!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.44,0:10:33.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.29,0:10:36.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you'd like, I can explain things at the front desk
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.71,0:10:38.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and get a spare key!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.81,0:10:43.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks! I'll keep watch here to make sure he doesn't escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.88,0:10:46.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll call for the police and an ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.55,0:10:48.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.12,0:10:52.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be faster to go directly to the nearby police box instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.56,0:10:53.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.35,0:10:55.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.83,0:11:03.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! Hijikata{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s wife, in Okita{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s room?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.77,0:11:05.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Does that mean...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.17,0:11:07.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We need the spare key!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.17,0:11:09.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad! I brought a policeman!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.61,0:11:13.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a spare key, don't you?! Come with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.45,0:11:20.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! It's not coming down!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.79,0:11:24.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this elevator out of order?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.36,0:11:26.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it shouldn't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.06,0:11:31.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No other choice! Let's use the stairs! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.27,0:11:32.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.47,0:11:36.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Let's go, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.00,0:11:36.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.97,0:11:39.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.07,0:11:41.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! I've been waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.94,0:11:43.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did anything happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.94,0:11:46.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been pounding on the door,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.08,0:11:48.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but there hasn't been so much as a peep.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.32,0:11:49.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The key, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.21,0:11:51.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.45,0:11:54.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's all the noise in front of my door?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.59,0:11:56.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.06,0:11:57.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.09,0:12:02.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Isami!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.43,0:12:04.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.30,0:12:07.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Say something! Isami! Isami!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.97,0:12:10.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isami! Isami!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.84,0:12:13.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use. She's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.41,0:12:15.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh no...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.61,0:12:18.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It appears she was strangled to death with a wire of some sort.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.78,0:12:22.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Something like fishing line, most likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.75,0:12:25.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems she died less than 30 minutes ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.32,0:12:29.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But what is she doing on my balcony?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.36,0:12:30.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't play dumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.66,0:12:35.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We saw her collapse on the balcony from your room!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.20,0:12:37.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who else could've done it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.73,0:12:40.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I had nothing to do with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.13,0:12:45.04,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The old guy's right. It definitely looks like he killed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.71,0:12:51.30,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}We just need to find the fishing line, expose his motive, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.72,0:12:57.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hijikata{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.78,0:13:03.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I know it must be hard, but leave her as-is until the examiners arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.02,0:13:05.29,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.29,0:13:07.45,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Could this incident be...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.63,0:13:17.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The deceased is Isami Hijikata{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, age 38.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.14,0:13:19.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Cause of death, suffocation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.47,0:13:22.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We can probably assume she was strangled to death
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.01,0:13:24.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,with thin rope or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.48,0:13:29.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, is it true you saw her when she was murdered?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.25,0:13:30.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.49,0:13:34.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say if it was right after she was murdered or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.02,0:13:39.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but Ran, Conan, her husband Kozaburo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, and I all saw her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.93,0:13:42.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We just happened to be on the balcony.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.43,0:13:47.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We heard a phone ring from Okita{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s apartment,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.57,0:13:49.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and when we glanced in that direction...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.87,0:13:55.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...Isami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} collapsed onto this balcony from inside the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.61,0:13:57.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably as a corpse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.75,0:13:59.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And then what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.18,0:14:02.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We rushed here immediately, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.52,0:14:05.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But the door was locked,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.15,0:14:08.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and there was no sound from inside, no matter how hard we knocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.89,0:14:12.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We left Hijikata{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} in front of the door to keep watch,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.09,0:14:16.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and I went to the front desk downstairs to get a spare key.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.40,0:14:19.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And, just as expected, when we went inside,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.23,0:14:22.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the body was here, on the balcony.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.64,0:14:25.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! I've had enough of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.57,0:14:29.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who's shocked to see Isami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} lying on my balcony!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.95,0:14:33.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nor do I remember anyone knocking on the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.28,0:14:36.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, why would I kill Isami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} anyway?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.55,0:14:38.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.82,0:14:42.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still trying to play innocent?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.26,0:14:46.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I watched the door hard enough to bore a hole in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.43,0:14:49.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who else could've done it but you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.53,0:14:51.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, now, Hijikata{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.97,0:14:53.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, Okita{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r},
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.37,0:14:58.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,could you tell us what you were doing between 4:00 and 4:30,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.67,0:15:00.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,when the murder took place?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.94,0:15:04.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was here at home, listening to music.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.31,0:15:08.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because Hijikata{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} told me to let him visit this evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.88,0:15:10.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hijikata{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.15,0:15:14.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I asked him to make some free time
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.16,0:15:18.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so I could see if the rumors about him and Isami were true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.53,0:15:23.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess the rumors might've been true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.40,0:15:26.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} came here before Hijikata{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.17,0:15:30.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so she and Okita{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} could get their story straight,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.87,0:15:33.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but it turned into an argument, and he killed her without thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.44,0:15:36.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you, she never came here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.41,0:15:40.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something else fishy about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.22,0:15:41.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.28,0:15:42.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.92,0:15:50.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hijikata{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} always plays famous warriors and swordsmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.29,0:15:56.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're stuck playing villains like thieves, spies, and love rivals.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.26,0:15:58.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that have to do with anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.37,0:16:01.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too much to be mere coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.24,0:16:07.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd say the same thing about how you always happen upon murders.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.74,0:16:11.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector! I found something like fishing line on the floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.05,0:16:12.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.35,0:16:15.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait! I've never seen that before!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.85,0:16:16.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.99,0:16:21.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,we have witnesses who saw the body fall onto the balcony from here,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.22,0:16:24.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and we found the murder weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.09,0:16:28.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can save your explanations for when we're back at the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.50,0:16:30.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now! You can't be serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.13,0:16:35.84,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}A scrape near her underarm!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.84,0:16:38.27,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}How did that get here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.27,0:16:44.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}! Don't stay over there! Hurry inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.08,0:16:47.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}. I guess there really are zombies, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.45,0:16:48.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.52,0:16:54.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, when this lady fell, her legs were still in the room!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.19,0:16:57.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But when we came here, her whole body was on the balcony!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.49,0:17:01.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, now that you mention it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.80,0:17:05.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That means she must've moved on her own...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.30,0:17:06.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this true?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.26,0:17:07.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.87,0:17:12.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When we saw her collapse, only her upper body was on the balcony.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.81,0:17:15.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The killer probably just moved it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.74,0:17:20.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He probably set the body against the balcony window.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.95,0:17:25.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It fell onto the balcony, which we saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.79,0:17:28.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Flustered by our pounding on the front door,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.66,0:17:34.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,he pulled the body onto the balcony to avoid trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.70,0:17:38.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I wrong, Okita{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, the killer?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.50,0:17:40.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.20,0:17:45.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If so, then the body was pulled onto the balcony rather violently.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.97,0:17:49.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The body has many scrapes on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.41,0:17:52.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So you must've been in quite a panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.88,0:17:54.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.88,0:17:59.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I just told you, Isami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} didn't come here! She never had before!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.85,0:18:04.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I tidied up because they said they were coming over today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.33,0:18:05.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right, old man?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.69,0:18:10.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. This is my first time in this apartment,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.63,0:18:13.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but I can't say for sure for Isami...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.97,0:18:17.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Then you're amazing, Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.57,0:18:22.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, you ran directly to the balcony where your wife was!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.48,0:18:27.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you've never been here!\NIt's almost like you're psychic!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.45,0:18:33.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, come to think of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.46,0:18:38.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He ran right past me and went straight to the balcony!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.43,0:18:44.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's easy, little boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.47,0:18:48.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All the rooms on the 5th floor and above have the same design,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.60,0:18:50.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,aside from the reverse layouts!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.91,0:18:53.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem quite well-informed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.48,0:18:58.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I own all the rooms on the 6th floor, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.91,0:19:01.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's only natural that you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.55,0:19:09.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright. For now, let's take Okita{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} in as a material witness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.02,0:19:10.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.93,0:19:13.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I ask that you two come as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.86,0:19:15.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Me, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.96,0:19:19.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing. He just wants to ask some questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.37,0:19:22.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's obvious who the killer is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.97,0:19:29.51,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}It's true that this looks like an open-and-shut case,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.51,0:19:31.58,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}but something bugs me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.58,0:19:35.92,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}That creepy smile he had when he was by Isami{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}'s dead body!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.92,0:19:40.89,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}But she did collapse before his very eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.89,0:19:45.26,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He could've set things up so she'd fall over on her own,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.26,0:19:50.43,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}but Okita{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} says he was in this apartment the entire time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.43,0:19:55.43,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I doubt he could sneak into the apartment with a dead body...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.31,0:20:02.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I answer it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.08,0:20:04.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait. I'll get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.15,0:20:08.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes? Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.52,0:20:10.62,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Oh, Inspector Megure?! It's Takagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.62,0:20:11.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.25,0:20:13.62,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I'm at the front desk downstairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.62,0:20:16.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's wrong? What's all that noise?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.29,0:20:17.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.34,0:20:19.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us in!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.43,0:20:25.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the newspaper reporters! They caught wind of the incident!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.00,0:20:25.61,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.61,0:20:28.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just please hurry down here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.07,0:20:31.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We've locked the entrance, but given how they are...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.24,0:20:35.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now! We can't have them get inside right now! Do something...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.58,0:20:40.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Say. Do you have any other phones in your home?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.32,0:20:42.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No. Just that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.38,0:20:47.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! They're here, too?! Where'd they come from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.49,0:20:49.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.92,0:20:53.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Alright! I'll be right down! Just wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.80,0:20:59.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How did the press find out so quickly?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.81,0:21:05.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not too surprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.74,0:21:11.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hijikata{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} {\i1}was{\i0} being hounded by reporters about the divorce.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.58,0:21:15.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyways, don't tell the reporters anything you shouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.78,0:21:17.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a decoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.55,0:21:20.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll divert everyone's attention before a panic happens,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.62,0:21:22.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so you can take Okita down to the station!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.89,0:21:25.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand the plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.96,0:21:29.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd hold off on taking him if I were you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.06,0:21:30.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-When did you get in here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.70,0:21:34.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, when we brought the spare key to the room,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.77,0:21:38.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okita{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} opened the door himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.27,0:21:43.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if he did hide her on the balcony,\Nshe'd be seen right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.31,0:21:47.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I was the killer, I'd hide her\Nsomewhere less obvious
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.42,0:21:50.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,or escape the moment the door was open!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.75,0:21:53.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so dumb! Shut up, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.49,0:21:54.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.42,0:21:58.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You were on the 5th floor balcony yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.09,0:22:00.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,when you saw her body come out of the room!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.97,0:22:10.77,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Now I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.77,0:22:13.54,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}So that's what happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.92,0:23:47.99,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.99,0:23:54.13,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The method Hijikata{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} used to lead us to a deceptive place!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.13,0:23:57.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going? You're the real killer...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.73,0:24:00.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...Kozaburo Hijikata{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.53,0:24:01.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.80,0:24:05.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, show some proof!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.47,0:24:08.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly. The proof is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.11,0:24:14.12,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.12,0:24:19.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's Hint: Black tea
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.12,0:24:20.86,Dialogue Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, the actor case is closed!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.86,0:24:22.86,Dialogue Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that person was the killer?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.86,0:24:24.14,Dialogue Top,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know?
